usage.inline: Use data_uri for inline favicons (faster loading)
usage.file: Use svg file for external favicon (better caching)
usage.example:
<!-- In your HTML <head> -->
<!-- Option 1: Inline (faster) -->
<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="data:image/svg+xml;base64,...">

<!-- Option 2: File (better caching) -->
<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="assets/favicons/company.svg">
